'''Guile Company''' was a unit of [[Clawdite/Legends|Clawdites]] during the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]]. The [[Changeling/Legends|shapeshifting]] Clawdites allied with the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] during the war, serving as an intelligence unit behind [[Yuuzhan Vong]] lines. Despite a high casualty rate, Guile Company kept receiving new volunteers. However, Clawdites who had children were disallowed into their ranks, though some hid the fact they had children from the unit. The company remained intact after the end of the War.

